[[File:Maundy_Thursday_07_washing_feet_diocese_St_Asaph.jpg|right]]的約翰戴維斯主教為民眾舉行濯足服事。]]

[[洗腳禮|濯足礼]]，是[[天主教會|天主教會]]（又稱羅馬公教會）、[[東方基督教|東方基督教]]（包含[[正教會|正教會]]、[[東方正統教會|東方正統教會]]與[[東方亞述教會|東方亞述教會]]等）、以及[[新教|新教]]（[[聖公宗|聖公宗]]固定舉行<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.anglicancommunion.org/acns/news.cfm/2008/3/13/ACNS4378 |title = Anglicans world-wide mark Holy Week and Easter |work = Anglican Communion News Service |publisher = The Anglican Communion Official Website |date = 2008-03-13 |language = en |accessdate = 2011-10-28 |archive-date = 2012-03-24 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120324094333/http://www.anglicancommunion.org/acns/news.cfm/2008/3/13/ACNS4378 |dead-url = no }}</ref>、其他教派沒有一定<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.kencollins.com/instructions/how-06.htm |title = How to conduct a foot-washing service |author = Ken Collin |publisher = Ken Collin's Web Site |language = en |accessdate = 2011-10-28 |archive-date = 2011-11-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111103124559/http://www.kencollins.com/instructions/how-06.htm |dead-url = no }}</ref>），在濯足節當天的重要儀式。[[20世紀|20世紀]]初期，皇室政權仍在時以前，[[奧匈帝國|奧匈帝國]]的[[哈布斯堡王朝|哈布斯堡王朝]]與[[西班牙王國|西班牙王國]]的[[西班牙波旁王朝|波旁王朝]]，也會在每年的濯足節，舉行濯足礼活動<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.hofburg-wien.at/en/things-to-know/tour-of-the-hofburg/room-e.html |title = Foot-washing ceremony (Room E) |publisher = Hofburg Wien Kaiserappartements |language=en |accessdate=2011-10-31}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |quote = Washing of Feet and Hands |work = The Catholic Encyclopedia |volume = vol.15 |url = http://www.newadvent.org/cathen/15557b.htm |title = Washing of Feet and Hands |author = Thurston, Herbert |publisher = Robert Appleton Company |location = New York |year = 1912 |language = en |accessdate = 2011-10-31 |archive-date = 2011-10-11 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111011153245/http://newadvent.org/cathen/15557b.htm |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

天主教會係據《羅馬彌撒禮儀（{{lang-la|Missale Romanum}}）》一書，自從[[1570年|1570年]]開始明訂，各地教會於濯足節當天的[[圣体礼仪|圣体礼仪]]後，應舉行濯足礼，後於[[1955年|1955年]]經[[庇護十二世|教宗庇護十二世]]修訂為在圣体礼仪中舉行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://nccbuscc.org/liturgy/q&a/general/feet.shtml |title=Holy Thursday Mandatum |publisher=UNITED STATES CONFERENCE OF CATHOLIC BISHOPS |language=en |accessdate=2011-10-11 |archive-date=2010-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100621084349/http://nccbuscc.org/liturgy/q%26a/general/feet.shtml |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。儀式的進行，會在適當地點放置椅子，供選定受洗的人坐在椅子上，人數沒有規定，然通常是十二人，由[[教役|教役]]帶領入坐，[[司祭|司祭]]在教役協助下，逐一替各人洗腳<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.catholic.org/featured/headline.php?ID=3155 |title=Washing of the Feet on Holy Thursday |publisher=Catholic Online |date=2006-03-29 |language=en |author=Father Edward McNamara |accessdate=2011-10-25 |archive-date=2017-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170918021257/http://www.catholic.org/featured/headline.php?ID=3155 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

東方基督教是在各區的大型或特定教堂，依循《聖經》記載，於濯足節當天「最後晚餐」儀式後，盛大進行濯足服事，由[[主教|主教]]或[[資深教牧|資深教牧]]，為十二名[[長老|長老]]或[[執事_(基督教)|執事]]洗腳，重演耶穌為[[十二門徒|十二門徒]]洗腳的故事<ref>{{cite web |url=http://lent.goarch.org/holy_thursday/learn/ |title=Great and Holy Thursday |publisher=Great Lent, Holy Week & Pascha |language=en |accessdate=2011-10-26 |archive-date=2011-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111119205959/http://lent.goarch.org/holy_thursday/learn/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.antiochian.org/midwest/Articles/Development_of_Holy_Week_Services.htm |title=The Historical Development of Holy Week Services In the Orthodox/Byzantine Rite |publisher=Antiochian Orthodox Christian Archdiocese |language=en |accessdate=2011-10-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111026185059/http://www.antiochian.org/midwest/Articles/Development_of_Holy_Week_Services.htm |archivedate=2011-10-26 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

